# --- Secrets / licenses (never commit) ---
# BC developer license: sensitive and re-issuable from BC. Kept on disk only,
# never in git history (so it can't leak if this repo is ever pushed).
DEV.bclicense
*.bclicense

# BC app packages / build artifacts
*.app

# Local DPAPI container-password cache (normally under %LOCALAPPDATA%; here for safety)
bc-container-password.xml

# --- Claude Code (kept local, never shared) ---
# CLAUDE.md and the .claude/ folder are the maintainer's own Claude Code
# instructions and settings. They stay on disk for local use but are not part
# of the shared repository.
CLAUDE.md
CLAUDE.local.md
.claude/

# --- Tooling / machine-local ---

# Per-user launcher settings (paths, container name, org, etc.). Created by
# copying Settings.template.json on first run; never committed so each teammate
# keeps their own values instead of inheriting someone else's.
ScriptLauncher/Config/Settings.json

# PartnerCore tool run output: timestamped findings dumps (findings-<ts>/).
# Local, regenerated on each tool run -- an artifact directory, not source.
.partnercore/

# --- OS / editor cruft ---
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.log
